  "text": "The CSVAC project focuses on the development of an experimental circumsporozoite protein vectored vaccine against malaria, prepared using the chimpanzee adenovirus 63 vector (ChAd63) [CITATION_1] . This pre-erythrocytic vaccine candidate is currently undergoing GMP production and a Phase I CT is planned to start in Q4 2011. The ChAd63 vector has several advantages:",
